I remembered all that Christine had told me of the Angel of Music . 
The air was The Resurrection of Lazarus , which old M. Daae used to play to us in his hours of melancholy and of faith . 
If Christine's Angel had existed , he could not have played better , that night , on the late musician's violin . 
