As you please , gentlemen . 
Giry took the envelope with the twenty notes inside it and made for the door . 
Giry a proceeding likely to strain his sight , but Mon MME . 
GIRY' charmin was prepared to go to any length to discover the truth . 
I am to slip it into your pocket when you least expect it , sir . 
in fact , I come and go as I please . 
