The ghost ! continued Richard , in a low voice , as though fearing lest he should be overheard by invisible ears . 
The ghost ! Suppose , all the same , it were a ghost who puts the magic envelopes on the table . 
who talks in Box Five . 
At that moment , the clock on the mantlepiece gave its warning click and the first stroke of twelve struck . 
The perspiration streamed from their foreheads . 
The twelfth stroke sounded strangely in their ears . 
When the clock stopped , they gave a sigh and rose from their chairs . 
I think we can go now , said Moncharmin . 
I think so , Richard a agreed . 
