All the water had to be exhausted , in the building of the Opera . 
And nevertheless the engineers had to leave a lake . 
The Persian touched a partition wall and said If I am not mistaken , this is a wall that might easily belong to the house on the lake . 
The work of constructing this double case took a whole year . 
It was the wall of the first inner case that the Persian struck when speaking to Raoul of the house on the lake . 
At the Persian's words , Raoul flung himself against the wall and listened eagerly . 
except distant steps sounding on the floor of the upper portions of the theater . 
