I have not been able to find the house on the lake , Erik having blocked up all the secret entrances . 
The letters are there to this day . 
Even so , I am convinced that it would be easy to reach it by draining the lake , as I have repeatedly requested the Ministry of Fine Arts to do . 
I was speaking about it to M. Dujardin Beaumetz , the under secretary for fine arts , only forty eight hours before the publication of this book . 
